    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;A web resource is routinely referenced by means of the URI with which it is directly accessed.  But cases exist where referencing a resource by means of a different URI is preferred.  This specification defines a link relation type that can be used to convey such a preference.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
